---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Starfield from '../../components/effects/Starfield';
import GridFloor from '../../components/effects/GridFloor.astro';
import { CommentSection } from '../../components/comments/CommentSection';
---

<BaseLayout title="示例文章" description="一篇用于测试评论系统与科幻风格排版的示例文章">
  <section class="relative -mx-6 -mt-12 min-h-screen overflow-hidden px-6 pt-24">
    <Starfield client:load />
    <GridFloor />

    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-[15%] top-[20%] h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 blur-[100px] animate-float" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[25%] right-[15%] h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-amber/10 blur-[120px] animate-float" style="animation-delay: -4s" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <article class="prose relative z-10 mx-auto">
      <header class="holo-card not-prose mb-10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-cyan/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 font-medium text-cyan">示例</span>
          <span class="text-muted" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <time class="text-dim" datetime="2024-01-15">2024年1月15日</time>
          <span class="text-muted" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="text-dim">5 分钟阅读</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-ink sm:text-4xl">
          科幻风格博客示例文章
        </h1>
      </header>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <p>这是一篇用于演示科幻风格博客排版与评论系统的示例文章。整站采用深色太空主题、全息玻璃卡片与青色霓虹光效，旨在提供沉浸式的阅读体验。</p>
        <ul>
          <li>深色太空背景与星空动效</li>
          <li>全息玻璃卡片与扫描线动画</li>
          <li>响应式网格布局与 3D 网格地面</li>
          <li>支持评论与回复的交互系统</li>
        </ul>
        <p>你可以在本页底部尝试发表评论，观察新评论的高亮、回复表单展开以及嵌套评论的层级展示效果。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-12">
        <CommentSection client:visible postId="example-post-id" />
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
